DFSD reproducibility code

This repository contains reproduction code for:
Out-of-Distribution Detection with Directed Feature Space Decomposition (DFSD).

Parts of the data/checkpoint organization, DenseNet checkpoint usage, RouteDICE/DICE model wrapper, and the DICE-based C-PP implementation are adapted from the official DICE repository:
https://github.com/deeplearning-wisc/dice

DICE paper:
Sun, Y., Guo, C., and Li, Y. DICE: Leveraging Sparsification for Out-of-Distribution Detection. ECCV 2022.

Please cite the original DICE work when using the DICE checkpoints or code paths derived from the DICE implementation. Users should also follow the license and usage terms of the upstream DICE repository and the corresponding datasets/checkpoints.
